Annotation: Telemetry was lost in mid-Sept-2014 and the buoy is suspected to have iced-over in mid-Feb-2015. No data available.
Telemetry was restarted but data fail basic QC tests and should not be used (e.g. pressure values around 0 dbar).
Instrument failed to send valid data.
